  "body": "As part of the refactor done in #149, we should use goroutines to make the entire flow of a notary's service concurrent. Right now, the following functions are blocking the rest of the services running in the ShardEthereum node:\r\n\r\n```go\r\n// Start the main routine for a notary.\r\nfunc (n *Notary) Start() error {\r\n\tlog.Info(\"Starting notary service\")\r\n\r\n\t// TODO: handle this better through goroutines. Right now, these methods\r\n\t// are blocking.\r\n\tif n.smcClient.DepositFlag() {\r\n\t\tif err := joinNotaryPool(n.smcClient); err != nil {\r\n\t\t\treturn err\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n\r\n\treturn subscribeBlockHeaders(n.smcClient)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nNamely, joinNotaryPool and subscribeBlockHeaders.\r\n",
